sentences: In June 2018 she announced the launch of her new music project under the stage name A Girl Called She.
In 2007, Donnelly joined the musical group Paradiso Girls, after auditioning in London.
The Paradiso Girls released their debut single "Patron Tequila", featuring Lil Jon and Eve in April 2009, which reached number 3 on the Billboard's Hot Dance Club chart.

She is best known as a member of the musical group Paradiso Girls and more recently as a TV host on Style Network, G4 and ENTV - where she is known as "Fuzzy" and covers everything from the Grammys to the Oscars.
The first single and video "I AM SHE" was released 30 Oct 2018.
Donnelly currently hosts liveAttack of the Show! and pre-recorded TV shows for the G4 Network owned by NBC Universal.
